    • hasCustomCoders

      protected boolean hasCustomCoders()
      Returns true iff an instance supports the MessageEncoder.encode(D) and MessageDecoder.decode(java.io.InputStream) operations. Should only be used by SpecificDatumReader/Writer to selectively use customEncode(org.apache.avro.io.Encoder) and customDecode(org.apache.avro.io.ResolvingDecoder) to optimize the (de)serialization of values.
